title: Taguig River
text: The Taguig River, (), is a <a href="river">river</a> in the <a href="Philippines">Philippines</a>, a <a href="tributary">tributary</a> of the <a href="Pasig%20River">Pasig River</a>. It eventually joins the <a href="Pateros%20River">Pateros River</a>, forming the common border between <a href="Pateros">Pateros</a> and <a href="Makati">Makati</a>.
